```python
def transform(lengths):
    max_len = tf.reduce_max(lengths)
    batch_size = tf.shape(lengths)[0]
    range_tensor = tf.range(max_len)
    sequence_masks = tf.expand_dims(range_tensor, axis=0) < tf.reshape(lengths, [batch_size, 1])
```

```python
def transform(in1):
    max_len = tf.reduce_max(in1)
    lengths = tf.expand_dims(in1, axis=-1)
    range_tensor = tf.range(max_len)
    mask = tf.less(range_tensor, lengths)
    padded_mask = tf.pad(mask, paddings=[[0, 0], [0, tf.maximum(0, tf.reduce_max(max_len - in1))]], mode='CONSTANT', constant_values=0)
    return tf.cast(padded_mask, tf.int32)
```
